description: GHP Specialty Care AB engages in the provision of healthcare services. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 738 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2008-10-03. The Company’s activities are divided into four business areas: Spine/Orthopaedics, which offers a chain of hospital spine care, including spine surgery and rehabilitation, as well as sports traumatology and prosthetic surgery; Gastro/Surgery, providing gastroenterology, general surgery, treatment and surgery of obesity, as well as diabetes care; Arrhythmia/New Specialities, which provides treatment of arrhythmia and maternal health care; and Dental, supplying dentistry service. The company operates in a range of countries, such as Sweden, Finland, Denmark and the United Arab Emirates. Furthermore, the Company is a parent of Global Health Partner Ltd.
